author: Sachs, Jeffrey D. and Andrew M. Warner

organization.description: Group for Economics data especially that which is [open data](http://opendefinition.org/). This can be any kind of data related to economics from development to finance, and micro to macro. We run an open group policy so anyone can add datasets to this group but we will review datasets added to the group for quality.
organization.title: Economics Datasets
organization.name: economics

name: natural-resource-abundance-and-economic-growth
notes:
The following files are associated with Jeffrey D. Sachs and Andrew M. Warner
"Natural Resource Abundance and Economic Growth", Revised, December 1997.

nr97.do is a program written in STATA (version 5) to run the regressions.
nr97.dta is the STATA data set with the data.
nr97.xls is an excel spreadsheet with the data (version 2.1).
nr97.html is an html file with the data.
title: Natural Resource Abundance and Economic Growth
